WEBVTT

00:00:00.507 --> 00:00:10.191
Characters, actions, places, occupations, and events in this series are fictional and created for entertainment purposes only.

00:00:10.191 --> 00:00:15.282
They are not intended to urge or promote any behavior in the series.

00:00:15.282 --> 00:00:18.114
Viewer discretion is advised.

00:00:18.703 --> 00:00:22.337
I'm still the same Wave, your boyfriend.

00:00:22.686 --> 00:00:25.108
Being your boyfriend is way better than being a prince.

00:00:25.893 --> 00:00:27.533
From now on, there will be no more secret places.

00:00:27.707 --> 00:00:29.763
Let's love each other openly, so the whole island knows.

00:00:30.308 --> 00:00:32.508
I'm not going anywhere.

00:00:32.661 --> 00:00:34.576
My heart belongs here.

00:00:50.902 --> 00:00:51.988
Take care of it for me.

00:00:56.087 --> 00:00:57.338
Who were you talking to?

00:01:01.023 --> 00:01:01.945
Victor.

00:01:02.577 --> 00:01:04.568
I asked him to help me find a new piano.

00:01:06.334 --> 00:01:08.957
Victor really seems to know
everything about you, huh?

00:01:15.084 --> 00:01:17.294
You know you can talk to me
about anything, right?

00:01:23.094 --> 00:01:25.460
Victor and I aren't like that.

00:01:26.267 --> 00:01:27.667
You don't have to worry.

00:01:28.910 --> 00:01:34.142
Besides, I know I could never be
that kind of person anyway.

00:01:37.020 --> 00:01:40.283
What kind of person? Tell me.

00:01:46.279 --> 00:01:47.930
Be a prince who likes men.

00:01:55.191 --> 00:01:57.735
I'm glad you decided to tell me.

00:01:58.346 --> 00:01:59.775
It's better than keeping it all inside.

00:02:04.354 --> 00:02:06.328
But I could never tell Father and Mother.

00:02:07.614 --> 00:02:11.446
They wouldn't want an heir
who breaks tradition.

00:02:13.169 --> 00:02:18.931
Honestly, the one
who should rule Arantha next is you.

00:02:20.283 --> 00:02:21.648
You're so much more capable than I am.

00:02:24.483 --> 00:02:28.966
No matter how capable I am,
a woman can't be Arantha's ruler.

00:02:29.141 --> 00:02:30.290
It's never happened before.

00:02:31.794 --> 00:02:33.552
If someone like you can't be,

00:02:34.163 --> 00:02:35.762
then how could someone like me ever be?

00:02:36.656 --> 00:02:37.741
Who would accept that?

00:02:40.096 --> 00:02:41.306
Even if no one else accepts it,

00:02:42.702 --> 00:02:44.588
you have to accept yourself first.

00:02:45.199 --> 00:02:46.931
This kind of matter takes time.

00:03:59.481 --> 00:04:00.261
Lava!

00:04:00.435 --> 00:04:01.539
The prince got shot?!

00:04:04.417 --> 00:04:05.573
How is he now?

00:04:06.576 --> 00:04:07.425
I don't know.

00:04:07.643 --> 00:04:08.724
The doctor's still helping him.

00:04:11.101 --> 00:04:12.941
What about you? Are you hurt?

00:04:14.991 --> 00:04:15.907
I'm fine.

00:04:16.954 --> 00:04:19.302
But I'll find whoever did this.

00:04:21.155 --> 00:04:22.484
Forget that for now.

00:04:23.596 --> 00:04:25.313
Just pray he's safe.

00:04:25.836 --> 00:04:28.210
We promised them
we'd take care of him the best we could.

00:04:29.693 --> 00:04:31.438
I'll go check on the patient.

00:04:34.883 --> 00:04:36.113
Then I'll go talk to the police.

00:04:36.680 --> 00:04:38.509
Maybe they can find the shooter.

00:04:43.153 --> 00:04:44.079
Holy crap!

00:04:45.344 --> 00:04:47.397
Wave is actually a prince?!

00:04:49.076 --> 00:04:51.891
Wave— uh, I mean, the prince—

00:04:51.891 --> 00:04:53.108
he'll be fine.

00:04:53.391 --> 00:04:55.800
But don't go after the gunman, okay?

00:04:55.800 --> 00:04:56.959
It's dangerous.

00:05:00.251 --> 00:05:04.887
Lava, don't be stupid and risk your life.

00:05:05.607 --> 00:05:07.410
You barely know him.

00:05:07.693 --> 00:05:10.091
The prince's business isn't your problem.

00:05:10.091 --> 00:05:11.081
Let the police handle it, okay?

00:05:11.081 --> 00:05:11.896
Listen to me.

00:05:11.896 --> 00:05:13.164
What the hell are you saying?

00:05:13.840 --> 00:05:16.564
The person in that room
is someone I've loved for three months!

00:05:16.826 --> 00:05:20.055
I'll protect him, no matter who he is.

00:05:21.189 --> 00:05:24.247
I'll make whoever hurt him pay for this.

00:05:29.515 --> 00:05:30.370
Calm down.

00:05:39.942 --> 00:05:40.835
Where is that jerk?

00:05:42.209 --> 00:05:43.955
Jerk? Who are you talking about?

00:05:44.326 --> 00:05:46.098
The guy who shot Prince Davin.

00:05:46.512 --> 00:05:48.691
You're the one
who told him he's still alive, right?

00:05:48.844 --> 00:05:49.473
Huh?!

00:05:50.018 --> 00:05:50.841
Prince who?

00:05:50.841 --> 00:05:51.512
What are you even talking about?

00:05:51.512 --> 00:05:52.308
I don't know anything!

00:05:52.395 --> 00:05:53.938
If you keep pretending to be dumb,

00:05:54.592 --> 00:05:55.782
I swear I'll stab you.

00:05:55.782 --> 00:05:56.792
I'm not kind.

00:05:56.792 --> 00:05:57.292
Hurry up!

00:05:58.164 --> 00:05:59.279
Hey, hey!

00:06:00.457 --> 00:06:01.689
Just tell him already.

00:06:01.689 --> 00:06:03.367
Look at him. He's serious.

00:06:05.853 --> 00:06:07.604
Love-crazed people will do anything.

00:06:08.302 --> 00:06:09.096
Tell him.

00:06:21.901 --> 00:06:22.415
Asshole!

00:06:22.415 --> 00:06:23.292
Hey!

00:06:28.678 --> 00:06:29.181
Let go!

00:06:30.707 --> 00:06:31.419
That's enough!

00:06:31.724 --> 00:06:32.414
Hey!

00:06:53.653 --> 00:06:54.195
Wave.

00:06:56.201 --> 00:06:56.833
Wave.

00:07:00.801 --> 00:07:03.072
Kratae called me and said you woke up,

00:07:03.072 --> 00:07:04.151
so I came right away.

00:07:04.849 --> 00:07:06.409
You've been unconscious for two days.

00:07:06.409 --> 00:07:07.540
I was so worried.

00:07:12.272 --> 00:07:13.368
I brought you some oranges.

00:07:13.695 --> 00:07:14.749
I even peeled them.

00:07:15.120 --> 00:07:15.990
Eat a little, okay?

00:07:31.995 --> 00:07:32.907
Who are you?

00:07:38.580 --> 00:07:39.558
I'm Lava.

00:07:41.978 --> 00:07:42.687
Lava who?

00:07:45.129 --> 00:07:46.225
I'm your boyfriend.

00:07:48.115 --> 00:07:48.884
Boyfriend?

00:07:50.955 --> 00:07:52.056
I've never had a boyfriend.

00:07:56.548 --> 00:08:00.293
My name is Davin, Prince of Arantha.

00:08:01.252 --> 00:08:02.612
So you remember now?

00:08:03.288 --> 00:08:04.528
You really don't recognize me?

00:08:12.290 --> 00:08:13.488
I don't know you.

00:08:20.632 --> 00:08:23.350
I came to this island with my friend Victor,

00:08:24.266 --> 00:08:25.878
but he attacked me in the middle of the sea.

00:08:27.339 --> 00:08:29.848
After that, I remembered nothing.

00:08:32.312 --> 00:08:35.957
Are you saying you don't remember anything from the past three months?

00:08:36.698 --> 00:08:39.912
Not even where you went,

00:08:39.912 --> 00:08:41.004
who you were with,

00:08:41.331 --> 00:08:42.202
or what happened?

00:08:45.167 --> 00:08:46.182
I don't know anything.

00:08:48.362 --> 00:08:49.393
What exactly happened?

00:08:50.767 --> 00:08:51.865
And who are all of you?

00:08:54.024 --> 00:08:55.043
How do you know me?

00:09:00.320 --> 00:09:02.081
I think Lava should be the one
to explain that.

00:09:56.073 --> 00:09:57.563
Hello, Prince Davin.

00:09:58.544 --> 00:10:00.685
The doctor's told me everything
about your condition.

00:10:01.361 --> 00:10:02.391
Please don't be alarmed.

00:10:04.484 --> 00:10:05.487
My name is Peng.

00:10:05.814 --> 00:10:08.319
I own Like Heaven Resort,

00:10:08.581 --> 00:10:10.173
and I'm also the village head here.

00:10:12.223 --> 00:10:13.596
I'm Lava's uncle.

00:10:14.163 --> 00:10:16.935
Uncle Peng was the one who saved your life.

00:10:18.941 --> 00:10:21.377
Thank you so much for saving me.

00:10:22.772 --> 00:10:24.116
I just gave you a place to stay.

00:10:24.901 --> 00:10:27.747
The one who really saved you was Lava.

00:10:29.753 --> 00:10:34.297
He took you to the hospital and cared for you the whole time you were here.

00:10:34.798 --> 00:10:38.490
While we wait for news from Arantha,
please rest here.

00:10:38.882 --> 00:10:41.378
I'll update you as soon as I hear anything.

00:10:41.858 --> 00:10:42.880
Thank you very much.

00:10:58.908 --> 00:11:00.332
Give it a try, okay?

00:11:01.248 --> 00:11:02.621
I don't even know how to help you.

00:11:49.290 --> 00:11:50.729
Did I really sleep in this room with you?

00:11:51.579 --> 00:11:52.123
Yes.

00:11:52.734 --> 00:11:53.975
We even shared the same bed.

00:12:01.323 --> 00:12:02.474
In this tiny bed?

00:12:02.757 --> 00:12:03.772
We had to squeeze in real close.

00:12:08.918 --> 00:12:09.878
Can I ask you something?

00:12:10.576 --> 00:12:11.295
Of course.

00:12:12.560 --> 00:12:14.453
You said we were dating.
How did that happen?

00:12:16.372 --> 00:12:17.424
When did it start?

00:12:19.735 --> 00:12:21.370
And how far did we go?

00:12:25.251 --> 00:12:27.724
It started after I saved your life.

00:12:28.553 --> 00:12:30.149
I brought you back here

00:12:30.803 --> 00:12:32.268
and gave you the name “Wave.”

00:12:32.922 --> 00:12:35.183
At first, I didn't even like you that much,

00:12:35.881 --> 00:12:39.853
but little by little I saw how cute you were,

00:12:42.251 --> 00:12:43.339
and then we kissed.

00:12:43.622 --> 00:12:44.301
Kissed?!

00:12:44.563 --> 00:12:45.682
More than a kiss, actually.

00:12:47.666 --> 00:12:48.509
We…

00:12:49.207 --> 00:12:49.707
Huh?!

00:12:50.056 --> 00:12:51.085
We did it in this room too.

00:12:51.521 --> 00:12:52.893
You and I…

00:13:09.634 --> 00:13:10.689
Prince, are you okay?

00:13:18.691 --> 00:13:19.543
You know what?

00:13:21.985 --> 00:13:25.211
You were my first kiss and my first time.

00:13:30.115 --> 00:13:31.349
I'm truly honored.

00:13:33.006 --> 00:13:36.055
Hey, but I can't remember anything.

00:13:37.363 --> 00:13:38.912
I don't feel anything for you.

00:13:40.111 --> 00:13:43.971
To me, you're just a stranger now.

00:13:53.455 --> 00:13:54.409
I'm sorry.

00:13:56.132 --> 00:13:56.846
It's okay.

00:13:58.045 --> 00:13:59.736
We can't undo the past anyway.

00:14:02.004 --> 00:14:03.429
Let's just say it never happened.

00:14:15.604 --> 00:14:17.367
You can sleep in this room if you want.

00:14:18.675 --> 00:14:20.096
Maybe it'll help you remember.

00:14:25.809 --> 00:14:28.276
It's fine. I don't want to trouble you.

00:14:29.475 --> 00:14:30.996
I'll stay at the resort.

00:14:31.476 --> 00:14:32.466
It's probably more convenient.

00:14:33.796 --> 00:14:34.822
Don't worry about it.

00:14:36.610 --> 00:14:38.332
This room is yours too.

00:14:40.839 --> 00:14:43.738
It's Wave's room, not mine.

00:15:04.355 --> 00:15:06.326
Who did you bring me to see?

00:15:08.039 --> 00:15:10.012
The one who stranded you on this island.

00:15:16.529 --> 00:15:17.135
Victor!

00:15:18.931 --> 00:15:19.850
Prince Davin!

00:15:22.524 --> 00:15:23.810
Please give me another chance.

00:15:25.230 --> 00:15:26.296
Another chance?

00:15:26.421 --> 00:15:28.227
You've tried to kill me twice.

00:15:29.459 --> 00:15:30.643
I didn't want to.

00:15:31.019 --> 00:15:32.441
It was my father's order.

00:15:34.049 --> 00:15:37.576
I actually wanted a free life like yours.

00:15:38.558 --> 00:15:41.836
I wanted to come here
to have good times with you.

00:15:42.337 --> 00:15:43.883
I wanted to bring you home.

00:15:44.823 --> 00:15:47.715
But I couldn't. My father ordered it.

00:15:49.052 --> 00:15:52.002
So please give me another chance.

00:15:54.509 --> 00:15:57.133
I'll help you and your family,

00:15:57.801 --> 00:16:00.079
and we'll forget everything
that happened on this island

00:16:00.183 --> 00:16:02.162
and start over in Arantha.

00:16:02.496 --> 00:16:04.561
Don't give scum like him another chance.

00:16:14.251 --> 00:16:15.586
Aside from my sister,

00:16:18.364 --> 00:16:20.189
you're the only one I trust the most.

00:16:22.716 --> 00:16:23.906
You know all my secrets.

00:16:25.869 --> 00:16:27.077
You know all my weaknesses.

00:16:28.873 --> 00:16:33.546
But you approached me to hurt me
and my family.

00:16:39.562 --> 00:16:42.919
Was it worth it? Our friendship?

00:16:51.855 --> 00:16:56.424
Trust isn't given easily.

00:17:00.852 --> 00:17:02.342
If you break it,

00:17:04.932 --> 00:17:06.435
you'll never get it back.

00:17:14.268 --> 00:17:15.819
Lava caught you,

00:17:16.425 --> 00:17:22.171
so I'll let him decide what to do.

00:17:38.129 --> 00:17:40.116
This is our best room here.

00:17:41.662 --> 00:17:43.205
Please rest however you like, Prince.

00:17:49.471 --> 00:17:50.470
Thanks a lot.

00:17:51.326 --> 00:17:52.657
This place is nice.

00:17:53.409 --> 00:17:54.426
The atmosphere is also good.

00:17:55.805 --> 00:17:56.527
I like it.

00:18:00.537 --> 00:18:03.594
You already contacted people
in Aranta for me, right?

00:18:05.244 --> 00:18:08.211
Yes. I've spoken to them.

00:18:08.754 --> 00:18:11.386
They said they'd send someone
to pick you up soon.

00:18:13.099 --> 00:18:17.389
Paolo said your family is safe now.

00:18:20.689 --> 00:18:21.629
Thanks a lot.

00:18:22.193 --> 00:18:24.268
Just hearing that makes me happy.

00:18:26.649 --> 00:18:29.598
If you need anything, call me anytime.

00:18:35.259 --> 00:18:40.134
I'll check the AC for you
to see if it's too cool or too warm.

00:18:46.526 --> 00:18:47.611
Is the temperature okay?

00:18:49.136 --> 00:18:49.823
Yes.

00:18:55.515 --> 00:18:56.426
What about the pillow?

00:18:56.551 --> 00:18:57.883
What kind of pillow do you like?

00:18:57.883 --> 00:18:58.816
Soft or firm?

00:18:58.920 --> 00:19:01.060
If it's too firm, I'll buy a new one for you.

00:19:02.167 --> 00:19:03.202
I can sleep like this.

00:19:05.521 --> 00:19:07.076
And the mattress —

00:19:08.329 --> 00:19:09.561
Is it too bouncy?

00:19:10.334 --> 00:19:12.843
If it's uncomfortable, I'll get you a new one.

00:19:13.846 --> 00:19:15.148
I can really sleep like this.

00:19:21.352 --> 00:19:22.197
Are you sure?

00:19:32.175 --> 00:19:36.268
If you need anything, call me.
I'm here 24/7.

00:19:38.002 --> 00:19:38.502
Mm.

00:19:55.073 --> 00:19:56.165
Ah — Prince.

00:19:56.165 --> 00:19:57.211
Thanks a lot.

00:20:10.764 --> 00:20:11.616
Hello.

00:20:11.783 --> 00:20:12.641
Hello.

00:20:13.683 --> 00:20:14.536
Doctor.

00:20:15.747 --> 00:20:16.528
What?

00:20:16.946 --> 00:20:17.953
I'm tired.

00:20:18.601 --> 00:20:19.215
You're tired already?

00:20:19.215 --> 00:20:20.515
Come here, I'll stretch you.

00:20:20.515 --> 00:20:21.015
Come on.

00:20:21.433 --> 00:20:22.207
You go ahead.

00:20:22.604 --> 00:20:23.443
I'll stretch you.

00:20:23.443 --> 00:20:24.269
Okay.

00:20:27.423 --> 00:20:28.082
It feels tight.

00:20:30.283 --> 00:20:31.618
Aren't you embarrassed in front of others?

00:20:32.642 --> 00:20:33.664
Why would I be?

00:20:33.831 --> 00:20:35.901
We're legally married.

00:20:41.499 --> 00:20:43.499
Well, poor Lava.

00:20:43.812 --> 00:20:45.005
The prince doesn't remember anything.

00:20:47.845 --> 00:20:48.524
Yeah.

00:20:49.506 --> 00:20:51.053
He has tried every possible way,

00:20:51.575 --> 00:20:54.387
but we don't know if it'll work.

00:20:55.431 --> 00:20:58.719
I think it depends on the prince
whether he wants to remember.

00:20:58.970 --> 00:21:00.076
Lava can't force him.

00:21:01.037 --> 00:21:03.282
Pushing might make him retreat.

00:21:13.329 --> 00:21:14.074
Hey.

00:21:16.142 --> 00:21:19.498
What would you do if this happened to me?

00:21:21.023 --> 00:21:22.041
Hm,

00:21:23.628 --> 00:21:24.691
that would be awful.

00:21:26.258 --> 00:21:30.631
But I'd start over and try my best
to make you love me.

00:21:32.114 --> 00:21:34.383
Pretend to be afraid of needles
so I can comfort you?

00:21:35.051 --> 00:21:36.769
That might not work.

00:21:39.672 --> 00:21:42.882
If it doesn't, I'll try other things.

00:21:43.683 --> 00:21:45.510
Today, I'll fake fear of needles.

00:21:45.949 --> 00:21:47.189
Tomorrow, I'll fake fear of blood.

00:21:47.837 --> 00:21:50.800
Next, I'll enroll in medical school

00:21:51.009 --> 00:21:52.829
so we'll be at the same hospital.

00:21:55.168 --> 00:21:56.919
I'll be close to you.

00:21:57.420 --> 00:21:59.068
I'll finally make you love me.

00:22:00.676 --> 00:22:02.175
You'll go that far?

00:22:06.415 --> 00:22:08.420
If it means I get to hug you like this,

00:22:09.715 --> 00:22:11.071
it's worth any cost.

00:22:13.912 --> 00:22:16.141
Such a sweet newlywed couple, Peng.

00:22:16.642 --> 00:22:17.503
Just a little.

00:22:18.130 --> 00:22:19.688
It took us a while to go public!

00:22:20.022 --> 00:22:21.286
Let's continue running.

00:22:21.599 --> 00:22:22.557
Come here.

00:22:22.557 --> 00:22:23.389
Come.

00:22:23.493 --> 00:22:25.327
You're not old. Come on, run.

00:22:25.327 --> 00:22:26.306
I'm already old.

00:23:12.733 --> 00:23:15.850
Does everyone have to be good at drawing
in architecture school?

00:23:18.691 --> 00:23:19.785
Not really.

00:23:21.101 --> 00:23:22.674
You just need the basics,

00:23:22.987 --> 00:23:24.693
like an understanding of building structures.

00:23:26.510 --> 00:23:28.263
But I don't draw people much.

00:23:28.911 --> 00:23:29.904
You're the first I've drawn.

00:23:35.147 --> 00:23:37.798
Is drawing me hard?

00:23:42.435 --> 00:23:43.268
Nope.

00:23:44.020 --> 00:23:46.481
Your eyes, nose, and mouth
have clear structures.

00:23:48.803 --> 00:23:49.823
I like your eyes.

00:23:50.053 --> 00:23:51.081
They're beautiful.

00:24:03.392 --> 00:24:04.090
What are you doing?

00:24:05.677 --> 00:24:06.930
I'm making my eyes big,

00:24:07.181 --> 00:24:08.662
so you'll draw them nicely.

00:24:12.129 --> 00:24:13.088
No need.

00:24:14.007 --> 00:24:15.556
I already remember your eyes.

00:24:16.475 --> 00:24:17.492
I've looked at them a lot.

00:24:44.092 --> 00:24:45.183
You picked flowers.

00:24:45.893 --> 00:24:47.306
Uncle Peng will scold you.

00:24:48.476 --> 00:24:49.505
It's fine.

00:24:50.153 --> 00:24:52.049
I thought you were handsome before,

00:24:52.362 --> 00:24:54.511
but now you're insanely handsome.

00:25:35.210 --> 00:25:36.197
Prince!

00:25:38.348 --> 00:25:39.108
Prince!

00:25:40.821 --> 00:25:41.834
Prince!

00:25:45.364 --> 00:25:46.546
What's going on, Lava?

00:25:47.006 --> 00:25:48.437
I heard a really loud explosion.

