00:45:37.920 --> 00:45:39.837
You were there when she was born.

00:45:39.837 --> 00:45:41.967
When my water broke!
Do you remember?

00:45:50.451 --> 00:45:53.167
Come here, sweet girl.

00:45:55.151 --> 00:45:56.889
Come see the Prince.

00:46:08.333 --> 00:46:10.808
Let the Prince hold you.

00:46:29.834 --> 00:46:32.024
Come on, come on. I'll carry her now.

00:46:36.827 --> 00:46:37.838
Hi there.

00:46:38.882 --> 00:46:41.925
Can I play with you? Peek-a-boo!

00:46:43.439 --> 00:46:44.533
Peek-a-boo!

00:46:51.006 --> 00:46:52.294
Chief.

00:46:53.730 --> 00:46:57.451
Well, I wanted to ask.

00:46:57.451 --> 00:47:04.430
Can you and Dr. Wut
adopt my daughter as your own?

00:47:04.430 --> 00:47:06.576
Dao, why?

00:47:07.072 --> 00:47:08.316
Where is her real father?

00:47:10.248 --> 00:47:13.710
I don't know where he is, and I don't care.

00:47:14.206 --> 00:47:15.727
I only care about my child.

00:47:16.092 --> 00:47:18.164
I'm scared I can't raise her well on my own.

00:47:18.295 --> 00:47:21.090
I want her to be in the care
of someone capable,

00:47:23.126 --> 00:47:31.990
so I think you both could be my child's dads and secure her future.

00:47:37.133 --> 00:47:38.921
I don't know about that, Dao.

00:47:39.547 --> 00:47:41.032
You have to ask Dr. Wut.

00:47:49.542 --> 00:47:51.029
I'm fine with that.

00:47:53.561 --> 00:47:55.433
We're legally married now.

00:47:57.626 --> 00:48:01.206
If another child joins the family, I'm ready.

00:48:02.329 --> 00:48:03.001
Right?

00:48:03.001 --> 00:48:04.949
Are you ready? Are you?

00:48:04.949 --> 00:48:05.665
Alright.

00:48:06.526 --> 00:48:08.415
Let's go file the papers at the district office.

00:48:10.403 --> 00:48:14.019
Chief, thank you so much!

00:48:14.019 --> 00:48:15.559
Thank you, Dr. Wut.

00:48:16.681 --> 00:48:18.698
I haven't even named her yet.

00:48:18.907 --> 00:48:21.554
I told you, Chief, you should name her.

00:48:21.789 --> 00:48:24.004
Let me and Dr.Wut think about it first.

00:48:24.422 --> 00:48:27.625
Or maybe the Prince
would like to name her?

00:48:32.943 --> 00:48:35.447
No, I'm an outsider.

00:48:36.126 --> 00:48:37.212
You should name her yourselves.

00:48:39.483 --> 00:48:40.971
You're not an outsider.

00:48:41.519 --> 00:48:43.278
You're also part of our family.

00:48:48.890 --> 00:48:51.068
You're such a chubby little girl.

00:48:51.068 --> 00:48:52.983
How lucky you are, my daughter.

00:48:53.479 --> 00:48:55.746
By the way, where is Lava?

00:48:56.738 --> 00:48:58.371
I want to ask him about that name.

00:48:58.684 --> 00:49:01.007
He's in his room, probably sleeping.

00:49:05.784 --> 00:49:07.278
Come on. I'll carry her.

00:49:09.079 --> 00:49:11.602
Come, sweetheart.

00:49:15.230 --> 00:49:16.823
Do you like it?

00:49:23.949 --> 00:49:24.723
Lava.

00:49:29.422 --> 00:49:30.230
Lava.

00:49:31.692 --> 00:49:33.350
I really don't know where that place is.

00:49:38.154 --> 00:49:39.251
Lava, are you in there?

00:49:41.522 --> 00:49:42.668
I'm coming in.

00:52:24.778 --> 00:52:25.940
I like your eyes.

00:52:26.123 --> 00:52:27.491
They're beautiful.

00:52:29.083 --> 00:52:31.585
But I don't draw people much.

00:52:31.898 --> 00:52:33.349
You're the first I've drawn.

00:52:43.417 --> 00:52:46.506
NAVA MAHASAMUT

00:52:48.647 --> 00:52:50.632
See you at Nava Mahasamut.

00:52:51.911 --> 00:52:54.207
You said you wanted a real name, right?

00:52:55.460 --> 00:52:57.429
I found one with a nice meaning.

00:52:57.429 --> 00:52:58.489
NAVA MAHASAMUT

00:54:03.387 --> 00:54:05.039
Ah! That tickles!

00:54:30.919 --> 00:54:31.681
Mr. Peng!

00:54:33.090 --> 00:54:33.704
Oh…

00:54:36.549 --> 00:54:37.985
Calm down, Your Highness.

00:54:38.220 --> 00:54:39.192
Is something wrong?

00:54:40.654 --> 00:54:41.993
I need your help.

00:55:41.502 --> 00:55:42.620
Why are you leaving so fast?

00:55:46.953 --> 00:55:48.069
You're not waiting for me anymore?

00:56:06.132 --> 00:56:07.489
Your secret code—

00:56:08.821 --> 00:56:10.050
it took time, you know.

00:56:12.452 --> 00:56:13.690
How did you even get here?

00:56:14.943 --> 00:56:15.726
Did you remember everything?

00:56:17.945 --> 00:56:18.707
Not yet.

00:56:22.403 --> 00:56:26.737
Just bits and pieces. It's still blurry.

00:56:33.420 --> 00:56:34.531
It's okay.

00:56:36.410 --> 00:56:38.074
I've done my best.

00:56:38.883 --> 00:56:43.808
Just the fact that you remember this island makes me happy enough.

00:56:45.844 --> 00:56:47.633
From what you've shown me,

00:56:48.964 --> 00:56:54.912
Lava and Wave must have shared
so many good memories together, right?

00:56:57.705 --> 00:57:02.528
It's a shame I'm the only one
who remembers them.

00:57:07.253 --> 00:57:09.314
I once said I envied Wave

00:57:11.898 --> 00:57:14.419
because he got to restart
his memories from zero.

00:57:16.403 --> 00:57:19.671
But not anymore.

00:57:21.263 --> 00:57:23.461
Now I want to remember
everything about us forever.

00:57:26.672 --> 00:57:27.910
I'm still trying.

00:57:29.450 --> 00:57:30.517
Just give me a little more time.

00:57:33.519 --> 00:57:35.003
Do I even have any left?

00:57:41.425 --> 00:57:42.381
It's fine.

00:57:43.164 --> 00:57:45.301
Even if I only have one day,

00:57:46.032 --> 00:57:48.774
one hour, or one minute left,

00:57:50.340 --> 00:57:53.043
I'll make you remember
what happened between us.

00:58:01.344 --> 00:58:02.866
Can I try something?

00:59:24.117 --> 00:59:25.335
It's a lot clearer now.

00:59:38.091 --> 00:59:38.985
Do you want a bite?

01:00:22.943 --> 01:00:24.000
Anya!

01:00:26.924 --> 01:00:30.258
If tonight is the last night we get to be together,

01:00:30.258 --> 01:00:32.643
can we make it a night we'll remember forever?

01:00:32.643 --> 01:00:35.593
What if I go to the palace to see you?

01:00:37.707 --> 01:00:41.321
What happened between us would just be a summer memory.

01:00:41.321 --> 01:00:42.963
Wave has nothing to lose.

01:00:42.963 --> 01:00:44.070
He has no past to hold on to.

01:00:44.070 --> 01:00:45.923
All his life, it's just you!